Installation & Setup Instructions
=================================

Install from PEAR channel
-------------------------

 $ pear channel-discover ex.floesive.org
 $ pear install floe/Floe


Install from download
---------------------

Download the .tgz release then copy all files into a location on your PHP
include_path (or copy to the directory lib/floe in your existing project).


Install from source
-------------------

Download the current HEAD from GitHub:

 $ git clone git@github.com:maetl/floe floe-dev

Add the floe-dev/src directory to your PHP include_path.

Run all development tests (requires SimpleTest):

 $ php tests/floe.suite.php

Run an individual test case:

 $ php tests/server.test.php

